OWASP (Open Web Application Security Project)
Use Spring Data JPA or JDBC templates with prepared statements to parameterize your database queries
Implement secure authentication and authorization mechanisms using Spring Security.(@EnableWebSecurity)
Ensure sensitive data is stored securely using encryption,Avoid logging sensitive data, and use HTTPS for secure communication.
Use tools like OWASP Dependency-Check to identify vulnerable dependencies.
Sanitize and validate user input. Use libraries like OWASP Java HTML Sanitizer to prevent XSS attacks.